The 2019 MyBroadband Cloud Conference has kicked off at the Gallagher Convention Centre in Midrand. Speakers at the conference include Liquid Telecom CEO Reshaad Sha, Connection Telecom CEO David Meintjes, Huawei Cloud and Data Center Solutions Director Marcus Tay, Microsoft Cloud Specialist Kevin George, and Siatik CEO Brett StClair. Delegates will also hear from Schneider Electric Regional Executive Derek Friend, Teraco Managing Director Jan Hnizdo, SAP Africa Channel and General Business Director Kathryn Tindale, and Oracle Solution Engineering Director Ocea Garriock. The panel discussion will feature VMWare’s Dave Funnell and Mimecast’s Mikey Molfessis. You can watch the conference live, below, thanks to our streaming partner Antfarm. 